             was indicted for that <rs id="t18210912-114-off660" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210912-114-off660" type="offenceCategory" value="miscellaneous"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210912-114-off660" type="offenceSubcategory" value="kidnapping"></interp>
               she, on the <rs id="t18210912-114-cd661" type="crimeDate">21st of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210912-114-off660 t18210912-114-cd661"></join>, maliciously and feloniously did take, decoy, and entice away, a certain female child, called 
                     
                        <persName id="t18210912-114-victim1254" type="victimName">
                           Hester Maria 
                           King
                        <interp inst="t18210912-114-victim1254" type="surname" value="King"></interp>
